oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Glenwood Baptist Church
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Offset printing;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: A black and white negative taped to and framed by a masking sheet advertising the Glenwood Baptist Church bond drive. The text says, "We're tearing the paper.. off the walls.. to tell you about our bond drive." The negative would have been used to create a corresponding printing plate.
